snippet.title: Rojo stress run to cameraman to play with while Torres see jealousy go play too
snippet.description:
HI Dear. Welcome to my channel Wild monkey lovely .  In this channel, you will see the daily life of all abandoned baby monkey called "Sovanna Team Or Family" that used to be home feed before. Everyday we go to see them bringing them fruits and milk cuz they still can't find any fruits on their own. They're all safe and healthy by our helps, guards and others parties. We try to do our best to protect and take care them all as much as we can. Please love and be kinds to animals.

Today I'd want to speak about all of the poor abandoned monkeys in the Sovana Team. I'm overjoyed to see the monkeys contentedly residing in Bayon with the Amari troop. Until now, all of the poor abandoned monkeys had 37.
